P_HTM[515]='*Dhātuyamakaṃ*';
P_HTM[516]='*Paṇṇattivāro*';
P_HTM[517]='**Aṭṭhārasa*  *dhātuyo* (yama. 1.dhāturamaka.1 ādayo) – cakkhudhātu sotadhātu ghānadhātu jivhādhātu kāyadhātu rūpadhātu saddadhātu gandhadhātu rasadhātu phoṭṭhabbadhātu cakkhuviññāṇadhātu sotaviññāṇadhātu ghānaviññāṇadhātu jivhāviññāṇadhātu kāyaviññāṇadhātu manodhātu manoviññāṇadhātu dhammadhātu.*';
P_HTM[518]='*Padasodhanavāro*';
P_HTM[519]='*Anulomaṃ*';
