P_HTM[643]='*Kāyo kāyasaṅkhāro, kāyasaṅkhāro kāyo.*';
P_HTM[644]='*Vacī vacīsaṅkhāro, vacīsaṅkhāro vacī.*';
P_HTM[645]='*Cittaṃ cittasaṅkhāro, cittasaṅkhāro cittaṃ.*';
