P_HTM[674]='*Saṅkhārayamakamātikā niṭṭhitā.*';
P_HTM[675]='*Anusayayamakaṃ*';
P_HTM[676]='**Sattānusayā*  (yama. 2.anusayayamaka.1) – kāmarāgānusayo paṭighānusayo mānānusayo diṭṭhānusayo vicikicchānusayo bhavarāgānusayo avijjānusayo.*';
P_HTM[677]='*Anusayayamakamātikā niṭṭhitā.*';
P_HTM[678]='*Cittayamakaṃ*';
P_HTM[679]='*Suddhacittasāmaññaṃ*';
P_HTM[680]='*Puggalavāro*';
P_HTM[681]='*1. Uppādanirodhakālasambhedavāro*';
P_HTM[682]='*Yassa  cittaṃ uppajjati na nirujjhati (yama. 2.cittayamaka.1 ādayo), tassa cittaṃ nirujjhissati na uppajjissati. Yassa vā pana cittaṃ nirujjhissati na uppajjissati, tassa cittaṃ uppajjati na nirujjhati.*';
P_HTM[683]='*Yassa cittaṃ na uppajjati nirujjhati, tassa cittaṃ na nirujjhissati uppajjissati. Yassa vā pana cittaṃ na nirujjhissati uppajjissati, tassa cittaṃ na uppajjati nirujjhati.*';
P_HTM[684]='*2. Uppāduppannavāro*';
P_HTM[685]='*Yassa cittaṃ uppajjati, tassa cittaṃ uppannaṃ. Yassa vā pana cittaṃ uppannaṃ, tassa cittaṃ uppajjati.*';
P_HTM[686]='*Yassa cittaṃ na uppajjati, tassa cittaṃ na uppannaṃ. Yassa vā pana cittaṃ na uppannaṃ, tassa cittaṃ na uppajjati.*';
P_HTM[687]='*3. Nirodhuppannavāro*';
P_HTM[688]='*Yassa  cittaṃ nirujjhati, tassa cittaṃ uppannaṃ. Yassa vā pana cittaṃ uppannaṃ, tassa cittaṃ nirujjhati.*';
P_HTM[689]='*Yassa  cittaṃ na nirujjhati, tassa cittaṃ na uppannaṃ. Yassa vā pana cittaṃ na uppannaṃ, tassa cittaṃ na nirujjhati.*';
P_HTM[690]='*4. Uppādavāro*';
P_HTM[691]='*Yassa cittaṃ uppajjati, tassa cittaṃ uppajjittha. Yassa vā pana cittaṃ uppajjittha, tassa cittaṃ uppajjati.*';
P_HTM[692]='*Yassa cittaṃ na uppajjati, tassa cittaṃ na uppajjittha. Yassa vā pana cittaṃ na uppajjittha, tassa cittaṃ na uppajjati.*';
P_HTM[693]='*Yassa cittaṃ uppajjati, tassa cittaṃ uppajjissati. Yassa vā pana cittaṃ uppajjissati, tassa cittaṃ uppajjati.*';
P_HTM[694]='*Yassa cittaṃ na uppajjati, tassa cittaṃ na uppajjissati. Yassa vā pana cittaṃ na uppajjissati, tassa cittaṃ na uppajjati.*';
P_HTM[695]='*Yassa cittaṃ uppajjittha, tassa cittaṃ uppajjissati. Yassa vā pana cittaṃ uppajjissati, tassa cittaṃ uppajjittha.*';
P_HTM[696]='*Yassa cittaṃ na uppajjittha, tassa cittaṃ na uppajjissati. Yassa vā pana cittaṃ na uppajjissati, tassa cittaṃ na uppajjittha.*';
P_HTM[697]='*5. Nirodhavāro*';
P_HTM[698]='*Yassa cittaṃ nirujjhati, tassa cittaṃ nirujjhittha. Yassa vā pana cittaṃ nirujjhittha, tassa cittaṃ nirujjhati.*';
P_HTM[699]='*Yassa cittaṃ na nirujjhati, tassa cittaṃ na nirujjhittha. Yassa vā pana cittaṃ na nirujjhittha, tassa cittaṃ na nirujjhati.*';
P_HTM[700]='*Yassa cittaṃ nirujjhati, tassa cittaṃ nirujjhissati. Yassa vā pana cittaṃ nirujjhissati, tassa cittaṃ nirujjhati.*';
P_HTM[701]='*Yassa  cittaṃ na nirujjhati, tassa cittaṃ na nirujjhissati. Yassa vā pana cittaṃ na nirujjhissati, tassa cittaṃ na nirujjhati.*';
P_HTM[702]='*Yassa cittaṃ nirujjhittha, tassa cittaṃ nirujjhissati. Yassa vā pana cittaṃ nirujjhissati, tassa cittaṃ nirujjhittha.*';
P_HTM[703]='*Yassa cittaṃ na nirujjhittha, tassa cittaṃ na nirujjhissati. Yassa vā pana cittaṃ na nirujjhissati, tassa cittaṃ na nirujjhittha.*';
