P_HTM[791]='*Na niruddhaṃ na nirujjhamānaṃ, na nirujjhamānaṃ na niruddhaṃ.*';
P_HTM[792]='*14. Atikkantakālavāro*';
P_HTM[793]='*Yaṃ cittaṃ uppajjamānaṃ khaṇaṃ khaṇaṃ vītikkantaṃ atikkantakālaṃ, nirujjhamānaṃ khaṇaṃ khaṇaṃ vītikkantaṃ atikkantakālaṃ taṃ cittaṃ. Yaṃ vā pana cittaṃ nirujjhamānaṃ khaṇaṃ khaṇaṃ vītikkantaṃ atikkantakālaṃ, uppajjamānaṃ khaṇaṃ khaṇaṃ vītikkantaṃ atikkantakālaṃ taṃ cittaṃ.*';
P_HTM[794]='*Yaṃ cittaṃ na uppajjamānaṃ khaṇaṃ khaṇaṃ vītikkantaṃ atikkantakālaṃ, na nirujjhamānaṃ khaṇaṃ khaṇaṃ vītikkantaṃ atikkantakālaṃ taṃ cittaṃ. Yaṃ vā  pana cittaṃ na nirujjhamānaṃ khaṇaṃ khaṇaṃ vītikkantaṃ atikkantakālaṃ, na uppajjamānaṃ khaṇaṃ khaṇaṃ vītikkantaṃ atikkantakālaṃ taṃ cittaṃ.*';
P_HTM[795]='*Suddhacittasāmaññaṃ*';
P_HTM[796]='*Puggaladhammavāro*';
P_HTM[797]='*1. Uppādanirodhakālasambhedavāro*';
P_HTM[798]='*Yassa  yaṃ cittaṃ uppajjati na nirujjhati, tassa taṃ cittaṃ nirujjhissati na uppajjissati. Yassa vā pana yaṃ cittaṃ nirujjhissati na uppajjissati, tassa taṃ cittaṃ uppajjati na nirujjhati.*';
P_HTM[799]='*Yassa yaṃ cittaṃ na uppajjati nirujjhati, tassa taṃ cittaṃ na nirujjhissati uppajjissati. Yassa vā pana yaṃ cittaṃ na nirujjhissati uppajjissati, tassa taṃ cittaṃ na uppajjati nirujjhati.*';
P_HTM[800]='*2. Uppāduppannavāro*';
P_HTM[801]='*Yassa yaṃ cittaṃ uppajjati, tassa taṃ cittaṃ uppannaṃ. Yassa vā pana yaṃ cittaṃ uppannaṃ, tassa taṃ cittaṃ uppajjati.*';
P_HTM[802]='*Yassa yaṃ cittaṃ na uppajjati, tassa taṃ cittaṃ na uppannaṃ. Yassa vā pana yaṃ cittaṃ na uppannaṃ, tassa taṃ cittaṃ na uppajjati.*';
P_HTM[803]='*3. Nirodhuppannavāro*';
P_HTM[804]='*Yassa yaṃ cittaṃ nirujjhati, tassa taṃ cittaṃ uppannaṃ. Yassa vā pana yaṃ cittaṃ uppannaṃ, tassa taṃ cittaṃ nirujjhati.*';
P_HTM[805]='*Yassa yaṃ cittaṃ na nirujjhati, tassa taṃ cittaṃ na uppannaṃ. Yassa vā pana yaṃ cittaṃ na uppannaṃ, tassa taṃ cittaṃ na nirujjhati.*';
P_HTM[806]='*4. Uppādavāro*';
P_HTM[807]='*Yassa  yaṃ cittaṃ uppajjati, tassa taṃ cittaṃ uppajjittha. Yassa vā pana yaṃ cittaṃ uppajjittha, tassa taṃ cittaṃ uppajjati.*';
P_HTM[808]='*Yassa  yaṃ cittaṃ na uppajjati, tassa taṃ cittaṃ na uppajjittha. Yassa vā pana yaṃ cittaṃ na uppajjittha, tassa taṃ cittaṃ na uppajjati.*';
P_HTM[809]='*Yassa yaṃ cittaṃ uppajjati, tassa taṃ cittaṃ uppajjissati. Yassa vā pana yaṃ cittaṃ uppajjissati, tassa taṃ cittaṃ uppajjati.*';
P_HTM[810]='*Yassa yaṃ cittaṃ na uppajjati, tassa taṃ cittaṃ na uppajjissati. Yassa vā pana yaṃ cittaṃ na uppajjissati, tassa taṃ cittaṃ na uppajjati.*';
P_HTM[811]='*Yassa yaṃ cittaṃ uppajjittha, tassa taṃ cittaṃ uppajjissati. Yassa vā pana yaṃ cittaṃ uppajjissati, tassa taṃ cittaṃ uppajjittha.*';
P_HTM[812]='*Yassa yaṃ cittaṃ na uppajjittha, tassa taṃ cittaṃ na uppajjissati. Yassa vā pana yaṃ cittaṃ na uppajjissati, tassa taṃ cittaṃ na uppajjittha.*';
P_HTM[813]='*5. Nirodhavāro*';
P_HTM[814]='*Yassa yaṃ cittaṃ nirujjhati, tassa taṃ cittaṃ nirujjhittha. Yassa vā pana yaṃ cittaṃ nirujjhittha, tassa taṃ cittaṃ nirujjhati.*';
P_HTM[815]='*Yassa yaṃ cittaṃ na nirujjhati, tassa taṃ cittaṃ na nirujjhittha. Yassa vā pana yaṃ cittaṃ na nirujjhittha, tassa taṃ cittaṃ na nirujjhati.*';
P_HTM[816]='*Yassa  yaṃ cittaṃ nirujjhati, tassa taṃ cittaṃ nirujjhissati. Yassa vā pana yaṃ cittaṃ nirujjhissati, tassa taṃ cittaṃ nirujjhati.*';
P_HTM[817]='*Yassa yaṃ cittaṃ na nirujjhati, tassa taṃ cittaṃ na nirujjhissati. Yassa vā pana yaṃ cittaṃ na nirujjhissati, tassa taṃ cittaṃ na nirujjhati.*';
P_HTM[818]='*Yassa yaṃ cittaṃ nirujjhittha, tassa taṃ cittaṃ nirujjhissati. Yassa vā pana yaṃ cittaṃ nirujjhissati, tassa taṃ cittaṃ nirujjhittha.*';
P_HTM[819]='*Yassa yaṃ cittaṃ na nirujjhittha, tassa taṃ cittaṃ na nirujjhissati. Yassa vā pana yaṃ cittaṃ na nirujjhissati, tassa taṃ cittaṃ na nirujjhittha.*';
P_HTM[820]='*6. Uppādanirodhavāro*';
P_HTM[821]='*Yassa  yaṃ cittaṃ uppajjati, tassa taṃ cittaṃ nirujjhittha. Yassa vā pana yaṃ cittaṃ nirujjhittha, tassa taṃ cittaṃ uppajjati.*';
P_HTM[822]='*Yassa yaṃ cittaṃ na uppajjati, tassa taṃ cittaṃ na nirujjhittha. Yassa vā pana yaṃ cittaṃ na nirujjhittha, tassa taṃ cittaṃ na uppajjati.*';
P_HTM[823]='*Yassa yaṃ cittaṃ uppajjati, tassa taṃ cittaṃ nirujjhissati. Yassa vā pana yaṃ cittaṃ nirujjhissati, tassa taṃ cittaṃ uppajjati.*';
P_HTM[824]='*Yassa yaṃ cittaṃ na uppajjati, tassa taṃ cittaṃ na nirujjhissati. Yassa vā pana yaṃ cittaṃ na nirujjhissati, tassa taṃ cittaṃ na uppajjati.*';
P_HTM[825]='*Yassa yaṃ cittaṃ uppajjittha, tassa taṃ cittaṃ nirujjhissati. Yassa vā pana yaṃ cittaṃ nirujjhissati, tassa taṃ cittaṃ uppajjittha.*';
P_HTM[826]='*Yassa  yaṃ cittaṃ na uppajjittha, tassa taṃ cittaṃ na nirujjhissati. Yassa vā pana yaṃ cittaṃ na nirujjhissati, tassa taṃ cittaṃ na uppajjittha.*';
P_HTM[827]='*7. Uppajjamānananirodhavāro*';
P_HTM[828]='*Yassa yaṃ cittaṃ uppajjati, tassa taṃ cittaṃ na nirujjhati. Yassa vā pana yaṃ cittaṃ na nirujjhati, tassa taṃ cittaṃ uppajjati.*';
P_HTM[829]='*Yassa yaṃ cittaṃ na uppajjati, tassa taṃ cittaṃ nirujjhati. Yassa vā pana yaṃ cittaṃ nirujjhati, tassa taṃ cittaṃ na uppajjati.*';
P_HTM[830]='*8. Uppajjamānuppannavāro*';
P_HTM[831]='*Yassa yaṃ cittaṃ uppajjamānaṃ, tassa taṃ cittaṃ uppannaṃ. Yassa vā pana yaṃ cittaṃ uppannaṃ, tassa taṃ cittaṃ uppajjamānaṃ.*';
P_HTM[832]='*Yassa yaṃ cittaṃ na uppajjamānaṃ, tassa taṃ cittaṃ na uppannaṃ. Yassa vā pana yaṃ cittaṃ na uppannaṃ, tassa taṃ cittaṃ na uppajjamānaṃ.*';
P_HTM[833]='*9. Nirujjhamānuppannavāro*';
P_HTM[834]='*Yassa  yaṃ cittaṃ nirujjhamānaṃ, tassa taṃ cittaṃ uppannaṃ. Yassa vā pana yaṃ cittaṃ uppannaṃ, tassa taṃ cittaṃ nirujjhamānaṃ.*';
P_HTM[835]='*Yassa yaṃ cittaṃ na nirujjhamānaṃ, tassa taṃ cittaṃ na uppannaṃ. Yassa vā pana yaṃ cittaṃ na uppannaṃ, tassa taṃ cittaṃ na nirujjhamānaṃ.*';
P_HTM[836]='*10. Uppannuppādavāro*';
P_HTM[837]='*Yassa  yaṃ cittaṃ uppannaṃ, tassa taṃ cittaṃ uppajjittha. Yassa vā pana yaṃ cittaṃ uppajjittha, tassa taṃ cittaṃ uppannaṃ.*';
P_HTM[838]='*Yassa yaṃ cittaṃ na uppannaṃ, tassa taṃ cittaṃ na uppajjittha. Yassa vā pana yaṃ cittaṃ na uppajjittha, tassa taṃ cittaṃ na uppannaṃ.*';
P_HTM[839]='*Yassa yaṃ cittaṃ uppannaṃ, tassa taṃ cittaṃ uppajjissati. Yassa vā pana yaṃ cittaṃ uppajjissati, tassa taṃ cittaṃ uppannaṃ.*';
P_HTM[840]='*Yassa yaṃ cittaṃ na uppannaṃ, tassa taṃ cittaṃ na uppajjissati, yassa vā pana yaṃ cittaṃ na uppajjissati, tassa taṃ cittaṃ na uppannaṃ.*';
P_HTM[841]='*11. Atītānāgatavāro*';
P_HTM[842]='*Yassa yaṃ cittaṃ uppajjittha, no ca tassa taṃ cittaṃ uppannaṃ, tassa taṃ cittaṃ uppajjissati. Yassa vā pana yaṃ cittaṃ uppajjissati, no ca tassa taṃ cittaṃ uppannaṃ, tassa taṃ cittaṃ uppajjittha.*';
P_HTM[843]='*Yassa yaṃ cittaṃ na uppajjittha, no ca tassa taṃ cittaṃ na uppannaṃ, tassa taṃ cittaṃ na uppajjissati. Yassa vā pana yaṃ cittaṃ na uppajjissati, no ca tassa taṃ cittaṃ na uppannaṃ, tassa taṃ cittaṃ na uppajjittha.*';
P_HTM[844]='*12. Uppannuppajjamānavāro*';
P_HTM[845]='*Uppannaṃ uppajjamānaṃ, uppajjamānaṃ uppannaṃ.*';
P_HTM[846]='*Na uppannaṃ na uppajjamānaṃ, na uppajjamānaṃ na uppannaṃ.*';
P_HTM[847]='*13. Niruddhanirujjhamānavāro*';
P_HTM[848]='*Niruddhaṃ  nirujjhamānaṃ, nirujjhamānaṃ niruddhaṃ.*';
P_HTM[849]='*Na niruddhaṃ na nirujjhamānaṃ, na nirujjhamānaṃ na niruddhaṃ.*';
P_HTM[850]='*14. Atikkantakālavāro*';
P_HTM[851]='*Yassa yaṃ cittaṃ uppajjamānaṃ khaṇaṃ khaṇaṃ vītikkantaṃ atikkantakālaṃ, nirujjhamānaṃ khaṇaṃ khaṇaṃ vītikkantaṃ atikkantakālaṃ tassa taṃ cittaṃ. Yassa vā pana yaṃ cittaṃ nirujjhamānaṃ khaṇaṃ khaṇaṃ vītikkantaṃ atikkantakālaṃ, uppajjamānaṃ khaṇaṃ khaṇaṃ vītikkantaṃ atikkantakālaṃ tassa taṃ cittaṃ.*';
P_HTM[852]='*Yassa yaṃ cittaṃ na uppajjamānaṃ khaṇaṃ khaṇaṃ vītikkantaṃ atikkantakālaṃ, na nirujjhamānaṃ khaṇaṃ khaṇaṃ vītikkantaṃ atikkantakālaṃ tassa taṃ cittaṃ. Yassa vā pana yaṃ cittaṃ na nirujjhamānaṃ khaṇaṃ khaṇaṃ vītikkantaṃ atikkantakālaṃ, na uppajjamānaṃ khaṇaṃ khaṇaṃ vītikkantaṃ atikkantakālaṃ tassa taṃ cittaṃ.*';
P_HTM[853]='*Suttantacittamissakaviseso*';
P_HTM[854]='*Yassa sarāgaṃ cittaṃ uppajjati…pe… yassa vītarāgaṃ cittaṃ uppajjati. Yassa sadosaṃ cittaṃ uppajjati. Yassa vītadosaṃ cittaṃ uppajjati. Yassa samohaṃ cittaṃ uppajjati. Yassa vītamohaṃ cittaṃ uppajjati. Yassa saṃkhittaṃ cittaṃ uppajjati. Yassa vikkhittaṃ cittaṃ uppajjati. Yassa mahaggataṃ cittaṃ uppajjati. Yassa amahaggataṃ cittaṃ uppajjati. Yassa sauttaraṃ cittaṃ uppajjati. Yassa anuttaraṃ cittaṃ uppajjati. Yassa samāhitaṃ cittaṃ uppajjati. Yassa asamāhitaṃ cittaṃ uppajjati. Yassa vimuttaṃ cittaṃ uppajjati. Yassa avimuttaṃ cittaṃ uppajjati.*';
P_HTM[855]='*Abhidhammacittamissakaviseso*';
P_HTM[856]='*Yassa  kusalaṃ cittaṃ uppajjati…pe… yassa akusalaṃ cittaṃ uppajjati. Yassa abyākataṃ cittaṃ uppajjati. Yassa sukhāya vedanāya sampayuttaṃ cittaṃ uppajjati.*';
P_HTM[857]='*(Etena upāyena yāva saraṇaaraṇā uddharitabbā.)*';
P_HTM[858]='*Yassa araṇaṃ cittaṃ uppajjati na nirujjhati, tassa araṇaṃ cittaṃ nirujjhissati na uppajjissati. Yassa vā pana araṇaṃ cittaṃ nirujjhissati na uppajjissati, tassa araṇaṃ cittaṃ uppajjati na nirujjhati.*';
P_HTM[859]='*Cittayamakamātikā niṭṭhitā.*';
P_HTM[860]='*Dhammayamakaṃ*';
P_HTM[861]='*Paṇṇattivāro*';
P_HTM[862]='*Padasodhanavāro*';
P_HTM[863]='*Anulomaṃ*';
P_HTM[864]='*Kusalā kusalā dhammā (yama. 3.dhammayamaka.1 ādayo). Kusalā dhammā kusalā.*';
P_HTM[865]='*Akusalā akusalā dhammā. Akusalā dhammā akusalā.*';
P_HTM[866]='*Abyākatā abyākatā dhammā. Abyākatā dhammā abyākatā.*';
P_HTM[867]='*Paccanīkaṃ*';
P_HTM[868]='*Na  kusalā na kusalā dhammā. Na kusalā dhammā na kusalā.*';
P_HTM[869]='*Na  akusalā na akusalā dhammā. Na akusalā dhammā na akusalā.*';
P_HTM[870]='*Na abyākatā na abyākatā dhammā. Na abyākatā dhammā na abyākatā.*';
P_HTM[871]='*Padasodhanamūlacakkavāro*';
P_HTM[872]='*Anulomaṃ*';
P_HTM[873]='*Kusalā kusalā dhammā. Dhammā akusalā dhammā.*';
P_HTM[874]='*Kusalā kusalā dhammā. Dhammā abyākatā dhammā.*';
P_HTM[875]='*Akusalā akusalā dhammā. Dhammā kusalā dhammā.*';
P_HTM[876]='*Akusalā akusalā dhammā. Dhammā abyākatā dhammā.*';
P_HTM[877]='*Abyākatā abyākatā dhammā. Dhammā kusalā dhammā.*';
P_HTM[878]='*Abyākatā abyākatā dhammā. Dhammā akusalā dhammā.*';
P_HTM[879]='*Paccanīkaṃ*';
P_HTM[880]='*Na kusalā na kusalā dhammā. Na dhammā na akusalā dhammā.*';
P_HTM[881]='*Na kusalā na kusalā dhammā. Na dhammā na abyākatā dhammā.*';
P_HTM[882]='*Na akusalā na akusalā dhammā. Na dhammā na kusalā dhammā.*';
P_HTM[883]='*Na akusalā na akusalā dhammā. Na dhammā na abyākatā dhammā.*';
P_HTM[884]='*Na abyākatā na abyākatā dhammā. Na dhammā na kusalā dhammā.*';
P_HTM[885]='*Na abyākatā na abyākatā dhammā. Na dhammā na akusalā dhammā.*';
P_HTM[886]='*Suddhadhammavāro*';
P_HTM[887]='*Anulomaṃ*';
P_HTM[888]='*Kusalā  dhammā. Dhammā kusalā.*';
P_HTM[889]='*Akusalā dhammā. Dhammā akusalā.*';
P_HTM[890]='*Abyākatā dhammā. Dhammā abyākatā.*';
P_HTM[891]='*Paccanīkaṃ*';
