P_HTM[906]='*Na akusalā na dhammā. Na dhammā na kusalā.*';
P_HTM[907]='*Na akusalā na dhammā. Na dhammā na abyākatā.*';
P_HTM[908]='*Na abyākatā na dhammā. Na dhammā na kusalā.*';
P_HTM[909]='*Na abyākatā na dhammā. Na dhammā na akusalā.*';
P_HTM[910]='*Dhammayamakamātikā niṭṭhitā.*';
P_HTM[911]='*Indriyayamakaṃ*';
P_HTM[912]='*Paṇṇattivāro*';
P_HTM[913]='**Bāvīsatindriyāni*  (yama. 3.indriyayamaka.1 ādayo) – cakkhundriyaṃ sotindriyaṃ ghānindriyaṃ jivhindriyaṃ kāyindriyaṃ manindriyaṃ itthindriyaṃ purisindriyaṃ jīvitindriyaṃ sukhindriyaṃ dukkhindriyaṃ somanassindriyaṃ domanassindriyaṃ upekkhindriyaṃ saddhindriyaṃ vīriyindriyaṃ satindriyaṃ samādhindriyaṃ paññindriyaṃ anaññātaññassāmītindriyaṃ aññindriyaṃ aññātāvindriyaṃ.*';
P_HTM[914]='*Padasodhanavāro*';
P_HTM[915]='*Anulomaṃ*';
P_HTM[916]='*Cakkhu  cakkhundriyaṃ, cakkhundriyaṃ cakkhu.*';
P_HTM[917]='*Sotaṃ sotindriyaṃ, sotindriyaṃ sotaṃ.*';
P_HTM[918]='*Ghānaṃ ghānindriyaṃ, ghānindriyaṃ ghānaṃ.*';
P_HTM[919]='*Jivhā jivhindriyaṃ, jivhindriyaṃ jivhā.*';
P_HTM[920]='*Kāyo kāyindriyaṃ, kāyindriyaṃ kāyo.*';
P_HTM[921]='*Mano manindriyaṃ, manindriyaṃ mano.*';
P_HTM[922]='*Itthī itthindriyaṃ, itthindriyaṃ itthī.*';
P_HTM[923]='*Puriso purisindriyaṃ, purisindriyaṃ puriso.*';
P_HTM[924]='*Jīvitaṃ jīvitindriyaṃ, jīvitindriyaṃ jīvitaṃ.*';
P_HTM[925]='*Sukhaṃ sukhindriyaṃ, sukhindriyaṃ sukhaṃ.*';
P_HTM[926]='*Dukkhaṃ dukkhindriyaṃ, dukkhindriyaṃ dukkhaṃ.*';
P_HTM[927]='*Somanassaṃ somanassindriyaṃ, somanassindriyaṃ somanassaṃ.*';
P_HTM[928]='*Domanassaṃ domanassindriyaṃ, domanassindriyaṃ domanassaṃ.*';
P_HTM[929]='*Upekkhā upekkhindriyaṃ, upekkhindriyaṃ upekkhā.*';
P_HTM[930]='*Saddhā saddhindriyaṃ, saddhindriyaṃ saddhā.*';
P_HTM[931]='*Vīriyaṃ vīriyindriyaṃ, vīriyindriyaṃ vīriyaṃ.*';
P_HTM[932]='*Sati  satindriyaṃ, satindriyaṃ sati.*';
P_HTM[933]='*Samādhi samādhindriyaṃ, samādhindriyaṃ samādhi.*';
P_HTM[934]='*Paññā paññindriyaṃ, paññindriyaṃ paññā.*';
P_HTM[935]='*Anaññātaññassāmīti anaññātaññassāmītindriyaṃ, anaññātaññassāmītindriyaṃ anaññātaññassāmīti.*';
P_HTM[936]='*Aññaṃ aññindriyaṃ, aññindriyaṃ aññaṃ.*';
P_HTM[937]='*Aññātāvī aññātāvindriyaṃ, aññātāvindriyaṃ aññātāvī.*';
P_HTM[938]='*Paccanīkaṃ*';
P_HTM[939]='*Na  cakkhu na cakkhundriyaṃ, na cakkhundriyaṃ na cakkhu.*';
P_HTM[940]='*Na sotaṃ na sotindriyaṃ, na sotindriyaṃ na sotaṃ.*';
P_HTM[941]='*Na ghānaṃ na ghānindriyaṃ, na ghānindriyaṃ na ghānaṃ.*';
P_HTM[942]='*Na jivhā na jivhindriyaṃ, na jivhindriyaṃ na jivhā.*';
P_HTM[943]='*Na kāyo na kāyindriyaṃ, na kāyindriyaṃ na kāyo.*';
P_HTM[944]='*Na mano na manindriyaṃ, na manindriyaṃ na mano.*';
P_HTM[945]='*Na itthī na itthindriyaṃ, na itthindriyaṃ na itthī.*';
P_HTM[946]='*Na puriso na purisindriyaṃ, na purisindriyaṃ na puriso.*';
P_HTM[947]='*Na jīvitaṃ na jīvitindriyaṃ, na jīvitindriyaṃ na jīvitaṃ.*';
